Class DynamicallyAnnotatedGraph<V,E>

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class DynamicallyAnnotatedGraph<V,E> extends Object implements AnnotatedGraph<V,E>
Class: DynamicallyAnnotatedGraph Represents an annotated graph whose vertices and edges carry dynamic annotations.

This class implements AnnotatedGraph, allowing annotations for vertices and edges.
